Patrick Poivey https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Patrick_Poivey 0 Patrick Poivey (born 18 February 1948) is a French actor. He is especially known for his voice: he is the French dub voice of Bruce Willis since 1988. Patrick_Poivey ( born 18_February_1948 ) is a_French_actor .
